member.summary:
Registers a callback method.

Example usage:

// Get the method info for a callback method
MethodInfo callbackMethod = typeof(MyClass).GetMethod(
    "MyCallbackMethod",
    BindingFlags.Public | BindingFlags.Static);

// Register the callback with Prime SDK
this.PrimeSDK.RegisterCallback(callbackMethod);

// Example callback method implementation
public static string MyCallbackMethod(string parameter)
{
    // Callback logic here
    return "Callback result";
}
